Mash about half a packet of Blu-Tack between your hands for about three minutes to mold it into a usable and bendable form. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/6/65/Craft-Blu-Tack-Jewelry-and-Accessories-Step-1Bullet1.jpg/v4-460px-Craft-Blu-Tack-Jewelry-and-Accessories-Step-1Bullet1.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/6/65/Craft-Blu-Tack-Jewelry-and-Accessories-Step-1Bullet1.jpg/v4-760px-Craft-Blu-Tack-Jewelry-and-Accessories-Step-1Bullet1.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Submerge the Blu-Tack lump in a bowl of 3 cups vinegar, 1 cup canola oil and strangely, a few pumps of conditioner. These ingredients will soften the Blu-Tack and give it clay-like qualities, allowing it to harden later. Leave the blu-Tack for about 30 minutes. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/8/8e/Craft-Blu-Tack-Jewelry-and-Accessories-Step-1Bullet2.jpg/v4-460px-Craft-Blu-Tack-Jewelry-and-Accessories-Step-1Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/8/8e/Craft-Blu-Tack-Jewelry-and-Accessories-Step-1Bullet2.jpg/v4-760px-Craft-Blu-Tack-Jewelry-and-Accessories-Step-1Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Dry the blue tack off and roll it out with a rolling pin into a thick but flat rectangle. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/6/65/Craft-Blu-Tack-Jewelry-and-Accessories-Step-1Bullet3.jpg/v4-460px-Craft-Blu-Tack-Jewelry-and-Accessories-Step-1Bullet3.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/6/65/Craft-Blu-Tack-Jewelry-and-Accessories-Step-1Bullet3.jpg/v4-760px-Craft-Blu-Tack-Jewelry-and-Accessories-Step-1Bullet3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
